253 program, as well as the program's employees and volunteer
254 advocates, are properly screened and adequately trained.
255 (m) The provisions of Section 45-39-81.02, relating to
256 Lauderdale County; Section 45-45-82, relating to Madison
257 County; Section 45-48-80, relating to Marshall County; and any
258 other local law from which funding may be distributed to a
259 local volunteer advocate program, shall not be superseded by
