261 (n) The provisions of this section shall complement the
262 provisions of Rule 6 of the Alabama Rules of Juvenile
263 Procedure and Rule 42 of the Alabama Rules of Judicial
264 Administration, both of which relate to the use of volunteers
265 in the Alabama judicial system, except that, in the event of a
